  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02720', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-099-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '何者不是水霧滅火設備之特性？', '["因水粒子相互之間存有空氣，而具有較佳之電氣絕緣作用", "水粒子細，易經加熱而蒸發膨脹，排開空氣，降低氧濃度", "具有將油類乳化之作用，減少油氣蒸發", "水霧粒子衝擊油膜面時可降低閃火點"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2166e65ae0a3", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099080", "c": "701", "s": "100", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年專技消防設備人員、地政士、專責報關、保險人員、特考中醫、語言治療、聽力考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02721', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-099-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '可燃物於無明火等火源之條件下，在大氣中僅因受熱而開始自行燃燒所需之最低溫度稱為：', '["自燃溫度", "閃火點", "沸點", "閃燃點"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2166e65ae0a3", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099080", "c": "701", "s": "100", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年專技消防設備人員、地政士、專責報關、保險人員、特考中醫、語言治療、聽力考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02722', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-099-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據閃火點資料，何者危險性最大？', '["汽油（閃火點< -30℃）", "二甲苯（0℃<閃火點< 30℃）", "正己烷（-30℃<閃火點< 0℃）", "松節油（30℃<閃火點< 65℃）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2166e65ae0a3", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099080", "c": "701", "s": "100", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年專技消防設備人員、地政士、專責報關、保險人員、特考中醫、語言治療、聽力考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02723', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-099-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於粉塵爆炸之敘述何者為非？', '["粉塵粒子直徑愈小愈易發火", "若空氣中氧濃度降低，爆炸下限濃度亦降低", "通常壓力溫度上升，粉塵的最小發火能量變小", "粉塵濃度愈高，發火溫度愈低"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2166e65ae0a3", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099080", "c": "701", "s": "100", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年專技消防設備人員、地政士、專責報關、保險人員、特考中醫、語言治療、聽力考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
